After moving a pile of rocks out of the way, leaving an opening big
enough for the robots, Hoist transforms. "We'd better see what caused
that." he says, quickly moving in, Ironhide follows, but is caught off
guard by Sunstreaker. "Let me go first, you can't lose your life over
something minor Ironhide, plus I can do a better job anyways. The three
Autobots enter the area to see the chaos the room has been reverted to.
Ironhide opens a channel. "Technobots, we need your assistance." he
calls on the silent frequency.
